    <!-- Visualization & Content Choices: Report Info: Investment Tiers -> Goal: Clarify pricing -> Viz/Presentation: Interactive Slider + Dynamic Bar Chart -> Interaction: User drags slider to select number of clients, chart and text update in real-time -> Justification: Makes pricing model easy to understand and engaging, far superior to a static table. -> Library/Method: Chart.js for the bar chart due to its simplicity and clean aesthetic. Vanilla JS for slider event handling and DOM manipulation. -->
